{"id": "art-2433", "label": "Art. 2433", "title": "Art. 2433", "slug": "art-2433", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1652302720\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1794\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1652302720\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 243<sup>3</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1033045671\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1793\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1033045671\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>exper&#355;i</span>, persoane fizice ori juridice, <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span> pe seama fiec&#259;reia dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> care particip&#259; la fuziune sau\ndivizare, dar independent de acestea, vor fi <span class=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span>\nde c&#259;tre registratorul de registrul <span class=SpellE>comertului</span>\npentru a examina proiectul de fuziune sau de divizare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na întocmi un raport scris c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_798231092\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1792\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_798231092\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Acest raport va preciza dac&#259; rata de schimb a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> sau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale este corect&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> rezonabil&#259;.\nRaportul va indica, de asemenea, metoda sau metodele folosite pentru a\ndetermina rata de schimb propus&#259;, va preciza dac&#259; metoda sau metodele\nfolosite sunt adecvate pentru cazul respectiv, va indica valorile <span\nclass=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span> prin aplicarea fiec&#259;reia dintre aceste\nmetode <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> va <span class=SpellE>con&#355;ine</span>\nopinia <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ilor</span> privind ponderea\natribuit&#259; metodelor în cauz&#259; pentru <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inerea</span>\nvalorii <span class=SpellE>re&#355;inute</span> în final. Raportul va descrie,\nde asemenea, orice <span class=SpellE>dificult&#259;&#355;i</span> deosebite în\nrealizarea evalu&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_46796615\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1791\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_46796615\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La cererea comun&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare particip&#259; la fuziune sau la divizare, registratorul de registrul <span\nclass=SpellE>comertului</span> desemneaz&#259; unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>exper&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionând</span>\npentru toate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> implicate, dar\nindependent de acestea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_338208623\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1790\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_338208623\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> în conformitate cu prezentul articol are\ndreptul de a <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span> de la oricare dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> care particip&#259; la fuziune sau la\ndivizare toate <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ndocumentele relevante <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de a face toate <span\nclass=SpellE>investiga&#355;iile</span> necesare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2024567200\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1789\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2024567200\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Examinarea proiectului de fuziune sau, dup&#259; caz, de\ndivizare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> întocmirea raportului prev&#259;zut\nla alin. (1) nu vor fi necesare dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torii</span>\naltor valori mobiliare care confer&#259; drepturi de vot la fiecare dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> participante la fuziune sau la\ndivizare decid astfel.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}